    "These were also executed in parallel to minimize technical variations that may confound the signal.",
    "There are many public Cell Painting datasets (for example, https://github.com/ broadinstitute/cellpainting-gallery) but we are aware only of one with genetic and chemical perturbation types run in parallel (RxRx3, https:// www.rxrx.ai/rxrx3).",
    "RxRx3 has not been provided with gene-compound relationship annotations and all but 733 genes are anonymized; any pairs that exist would be scattered across many plates and batches.",
